Alpha.title: Version 0.1.0

v0.1.0.description:
Changelog
- Fixed datapackage issue where items were no longer sent properly
- Fixed issue where time on bomb doesn't match time on mission information
- Fixed issue with Factory mode where pressing the retry button would stop sending checks
- Fixed issue with Factory mode where pressing retry on the last mission would auto-complete the mission
- Added RuleSeed support (in YAML)

[Information Page](https://github.com/GreenPower713/Archipelago/blob/main/worlds/ktane/docs/en_Keep%20Talking%20and%20Nobody%20Explodes.md)
[Setup Guide](https://github.com/GreenPower713/Archipelago/blob/main/worlds/ktane/docs/setup_en.md)
v0.1.0.title: Version 0.1.1

v0.1.2.description:
Changelog:
- Added Random RuleSeed support (in YAML)
- Fixed bug with collect that showed bombs as completed when only the last check was done
- Changed documentation to adapt to Archipelago 0.5.0
- Created an [Expert Manuals Client](https://github.com/GreenPower713/KTaNE-Archipelago-Expert-Manuals/releases/tag/v0.1.2) that can connect to Archipelago to get the needed manuals to solve the bombs

[Information Page](https://github.com/GreenPower713/Archipelago/blob/main/worlds/ktane/docs/en_Keep%20Talking%20and%20Nobody%20Explodes.md)
[Setup Guide](https://github.com/GreenPower713/Archipelago/blob/main/worlds/ktane/docs/setup_en.md)
v0.1.2.title: Version 0.1.2

v0.1.3.description:
Changelog:
- Fixed bug with Serial Number Modifier that was hiding the serial number instead of the RuleSeed
- Added Appendices section in the [Expert Manuals Client](https://github.com/GreenPower713/KTaNE-Archipelago-Expert-Manuals/releases) to show all possible vanilla ports.
- Added auto-completion for the connection screen in game based on your previously entered data.
- Added support to remove hardlock modules as a setting

v0.2.0.description:
Changelog:


- Added full support for MacOS
- Added OHKO Mode
- Changed name of bomb 2.1 from "Double Trouble" to "Make it Double"
- Changed logic for bomb 6,1 The Final Challenge; it nows requires 7 Time++ instead of 6
- Changed logic for bomb 2.6 Speedster I; it is now 1 [Button, Wires, Keypad], 1 Memory and 1 [WoF, Simon, Maze]
- Added support for Unicode characters in the Expert Manuals
- Fixed Last bomb never being considered in logic in-game when "Hardlock Modules" was on
- Fixed the rule seed showing with Solve-Explode-Retry
- Added In-game Text for checks
- Added a warning in-game when the rule seed should be randomized but the Rule Seed mod wasn't found
- Added a text for reason that a bomb is locked

Manuals can be found [here](https://github.com/GreenPower713/KTaNE-Archipelago-Expert-Manuals/releases)

[Information Page](https://github.com/GreenPower713/Archipelago/blob/main/worlds/ktane/docs/en_Keep%20Talking%20and%20Nobody%20Explodes.md)
[Setup Guide](https://github.com/GreenPower713/Archipelago/blob/main/worlds/ktane/docs/setup_en.md)
